description: Crave-It is serving delicious Italian American Cuisine to the streets of Jupiter and the surrounding areas. With delicious meatballs, pastas, crostatas, chicken cutlets  and the famous GODFATHER Sundae this truck won't disappoint!  Fried eggplant, and the vegetarian GODMOTHER sundae and much more.  Taste and see why we are South Florida's favorite Italian American Food Truck!🇮🇹🍴🇮🇹So stop by, and develop your own craving!
name: Crave-It
